1
00:00:00,040 --> 00:00:01,710
Who is it?

2
00:00:02,170 --> 00:00:04,300
You...

3
00:00:04,300 --> 00:00:07,170
You've fallen for someone else, haven't you?
Someone other than me.

4
00:00:07,630 --> 00:00:09,180
What?

5
00:00:09,880 --> 00:00:12,010
Are you in love with Wakami-san?

6
00:00:12,180 --> 00:00:14,310
Wait, what are you talking about?

7
00:00:14,760 --> 00:00:17,180
You've been avoiding me.

8
00:00:17,180 --> 00:00:19,980
You two look so happy together,
flirting like that.

9
00:00:20,230 --> 00:00:22,270
No, we weren't flirting.

10
00:00:22,270 --> 00:00:24,150
What else did you two do?

11
00:00:24,440 --> 00:00:26,400
Nothing.

12
00:00:26,940 --> 00:00:29,530
What kind of nonsense
have you been spouting?

13
00:00:29,990 --> 00:00:31,870
I did it...

14
00:00:31,870 --> 00:00:33,620
for your future.

15
00:00:34,580 --> 00:00:36,080
For my sake?

16
00:00:36,950 --> 00:00:38,870
Your manager told me.

17
00:00:39,540 --> 00:00:41,790
I've been thinking a lot about it, too.

18
00:00:49,920 --> 00:00:51,430
What's this?

19
00:00:52,220 --> 00:00:53,510
Open it.

20
00:00:58,520 --> 00:01:00,940
I was going to give this to you
on our anniversary.

21
00:01:01,730 --> 00:01:03,480
It's the key to my place.

22
00:01:06,070 --> 00:01:07,690
Let's move in together.

23
00:01:08,570 --> 00:01:10,360
Wait, why?

24
00:01:10,950 --> 00:01:13,280
Once you make it big,

25
00:01:16,530 --> 00:01:19,200
it won't be good for us to meet outside.

26
00:01:20,500 --> 00:01:23,880
I've given it a lot of thought.

27
00:01:25,670 --> 00:01:28,920
If we live together,

28
00:01:28,920 --> 00:01:32,550
we'll get to see each other more.

29
00:01:34,340 --> 00:01:39,470
It's not a big place, but...

30
00:01:40,350 --> 00:01:41,730
I see.

31
00:01:41,730 --> 00:01:44,060
Thank you.

32
00:01:44,440 --> 00:01:46,650
But what about Wakami-san?

33
00:01:47,110 --> 00:01:50,150
I told you, there's nothing going on.

34
00:01:51,690 --> 00:01:53,150
Ouch!

35
00:01:53,150 --> 00:01:54,490
Hahaha.
